proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.description

Class OutputColSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.description.OutputColSpec

  • public class OutputColSpec
extends java.lang.Object
    The third level of the Description Package, together with InputParSpec. An OutputColSpec describes one output column of an API.
